<p>출력값은 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Jimmy won't you please come home? The grass is green and the buffaloes roam</code></p>

<p>변수 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">jimmy</code>에서 개행문자 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">\n</code>을 찾아 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">replaceSubrange(_:with:)</code>로 띄어쓰기로 변환을 반복</p>
